title: Ep.11: Apple Cup Preview, Packers Loss, Jonathan Taylor, Buffalo Bills Struggles, and More.
description: Happy Thanksgiving everyone! In this episode we talk about our apple cup predictions, what the packers loss means for them, Jonathan Taylor's huge game, are the bills contenders or pretenders amidst their recent struggles, and much more.
